			======================================
				 Installing avfltctl
			======================================

1. Requirements
	
	* Installed AVFlt Control Library - libavfltctl, please see the
	  libavfltctl INSTALL file

2. Download
	
	* Get the latest stable version at
	  http://www.redirfs.org/packages/avfltctl-x.y.tar.gz

3. Compilation
	
	* Unpack package
		$ tar -xvzf avfltctl-x.y.tar.gz

	* Change to the avfltctl-x.y directory
		$ cd avfltctl-x.y

	* Run make command
		$ make

4. Installation/Uninstallation

	* Change user to root
		$ su

	* Install avfltctl 
		# make install

	* Uninstall avfltctl
		# make uninstall

5. Problems & Bugs

	* RedirFS's bugzilla
	  http://www.redirfs.org/cgi-bin/bugzilla/index.cgi
	
	* RedirFS's mailing lists
	  http://www.redirfs.org/tiki-index.php?page=redirfs_maillists
